videos.headline: Encalade makes a couple defenders miss for TD
videos.description: Terren Encalade spins his way to the endzone for the 30-yard TD.

videos.headline: Banks keeps on the option for the TD
videos.description: Jonathan Banks runs it in for the easy score.

videos.headline: Banks finds Hilliard who does the rest
videos.description: Jonathan Banks passes to Dontrell Hilliard for a 62-yard TD.

videos.headline: Mooney adds to the Tulane lead
videos.description: Jonathan Banks finds Darnell Mooney for the 19-yard TD strike.

videos.headline: Grambling gets on the scoreboard and Carter celebrates accordingly
videos.description: Martez Carter gets the edge and finds the endzone for the Tigers.

videos.headline: Grambling cannot catch Encalade
videos.description: Terren Encalade easily runs 58 yds for a TD.

videos.headline: Carter runs away from the defense for the TD
videos.description: Martez Carter sprints for his second score of the game.
